# Design Language
- Primary Color: Emerald Green (Tailwind colors.emerald)
- Aesthetic: Minimalist, Technical Blog, "ssp.sh" style.
- Typography: Inter for body, JetBrains Mono for code.
- Spacing: Generous negative space, max-width 3xl for content.
- Components: Subtle borders instead of shadows. No "salesy" or "flashy" gradients.
- Headings: Use emerald-900 for strong contrast.
- Links: emerald-600 with underline-offset-4.
- Code blocks: bg-gray-50 (light) / bg-gray-900 (dark), border-gray-100 / border-gray-800.
- Edges: rounded-md or sharp; avoid heavy rounding.
